Scene - Bad ending

Info: 

post-demo, animated, lyrics

Script:

The bad ending is a ramification that comes from the Scene - Apfel against Mantana if Apfel does not succeed, Mantana will continue with their plan, while Apfel dies laying on the ground, she sees her life past right in front of her eyes and what's about to come, like a slideshow she sees how the loop repeats once again, and every time the loop finishes it loops back faster and faster, until Apfel finally dies and is born again from the apple tree, thousands of years later.
